OL,3,CHigher fines for school absences in
OL,4,Cgovernment attendance drive
OL,6,FParents in England who take their
OL,7,Fchildren out of class without
OL,8,Fpermission will face higher fines as
OL,9,Fpart of a drive to boost school
OL,10,Fattendance following the pandemic.
OL,12,FThe Department for Education (DfE) has
OL,13,Fsaid a fine must be considered if a
OL,14,Fchild misses five days of school for
OL,15,Funauthorised absence.
OL,17,FSchool absence fines currently start
OL,18,Fat #60, rising to #120 if they are not
OL,19,Fpaid within 21 days. But the DfE has
OL,20,Fsaid fines will now start at #80,
OL,21,Frising to #160.
