OL,3,CHigher fines for school absences in
OL,4,Cgovernment attendance drive
OL,6,FIt comes after nearly 400,000 penalty
OL,7,Fnotices were issued to parents in
OL,8,FEngland in 2022-23 for unauthorised
OL,9,Fschool absences ` which was much
OL,10,Fhigher than pre-pandemic levels.
OL,12,FNearly nine in ten (89.3%) of the
OL,13,Ffines were for unauthorised holidays
OL,14,Fas families looked to book cheaper
OL,15,Fvacations outside school term times,
OL,16,Faccording to DfE figures released in
OL,17,FDecember.
