OL,6,FGovernment guidance is expected to
OL,7,Fclarify when financial penalties for
OL,8,Fschool absences should be used to
OL,9,Fensure councils issue fines
OL,10,Fappropriately.
OL,12,FThe DfE has said school absence fines
OL,13,Fwill be brought under a national
OL,14,Fframework to help tackle
OL,15,Finconsistencies in their use across
OL,16,FEngland.
