OL,6,FIt is understood the higher fines for
OL,7,Fabsences will come into effect from
OL,8,FSeptember.
OL,10,FThe DfE hopes the data set will help
OL,11,Fschools spot and support children at
OL,12,Frisk of persistent absence, or in
OL,13,Fdanger of becoming missing from
OL,14,Feducation.
OL,16,FRob Tarn, chief executive of Northern
OL,17,FEducation Trust and founder of
OL,18,FEngland's first attendance hub, has
OL,19,Falso been appointed by the DfE as the
OL,20,Fnew national attendance ambassador.
