OL,6,FHe added: "What is really needed to
OL,7,Ftackle poor attendance is more
OL,8,Ftargeted resources to find out the
OL,9,Freasons behind absence, including
OL,10,Fsupport for vulnerable families and
OL,11,Ffor children and young people's mental
OL,12,Fhealth.
OL,14,F"Without that work, higher fines could
OL,15,Fjust be further punishing already
OL,16,Fstruggling families and children."
